snippet.title: DCS IRAQ | Early Access Launch
snippet.description:
This week we unveiled the highly anticipated DCS: Iraq map, a monumental addition to our World. This map captures the rich history, diverse geography, and pivotal air combat zones, offering unparalleled opportunities for both historical and modern aerial warfare.

DCS e-shop: https://www.digitalcombatsimulator.com/en/shop/
